runs.text: Sotomayor's dissent unlike anything Katyal has seen before

"I've never seen language like this in a Supreme Court opinion." Former Acting U.S. Solicitor General Neal Katyal reacts to Justice Sonia Sotomayor's scathing dissent in the Trump immunity case and says this opinion makes the stakes of the November election clear.
